{"title":"Marin Launches New Four Corners 2 an Affordable Up-Spec’d Adventure Tourer","link":"https://bikerumor.com/marin-four-corners-2-adventure-touring-bike/","date":1708961735000,"content":"<p><img width=\"1280\" height=\"834\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-hero.jpeg\" alt=\"Marin Bikes Four Corners 2 hero\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-hero.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-hero-297x194.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-hero-800x521.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-hero-120x78.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-hero-768x500.jpeg 768w\" /></p>\n<p><br />Remember just last month when I told you about the newly upgraded Marin Four Corners 1 <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/updated-marin-four-corners-adventure-touring-bike/\" target=\"_blank\">Utilitour bikes</a>? Well, today Petaluma, Califonia’s <a href=\"https://www.marinbikes.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Marin Bikes</a> is bringing back its new <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/soc15-marin-celebrates-30-years-with-27-pine-mountain-1-four-corners-touring-rig-plus-vintage-collection/\" target=\"_blank\">Four Corners</a> 2 Adventure Touring bike after seven years of hibernation. The Four Corners 2 is a step up from the Four Corners 1, so Let’s check out the up-spec version. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Marin’s Four Corners 2</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-adventure-ready.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-adventure-ready.jpeg\" alt=\"Marin Bikes Four Corners 2 adventure ready\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-adventure-ready.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-adventure-ready-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-adventure-ready-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-adventure-ready-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-adventure-ready-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-adventure-ready-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos/Marin Bikes)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Well, first, this upscale model has been out of circulation for 7 years. It’s aimed at the more discriminating rider with the higher-end, Series 3 double-butted CroMo frame and fork with front and rear thru-axles. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-SRAM-Apex-drivetrain.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-SRAM-Apex-drivetrain.jpeg\" alt=\"Marin Bikes Four Corners 2 SRAM Apex drivetrain\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-SRAM-Apex-drivetrain.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-SRAM-Apex-drivetrain-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-SRAM-Apex-drivetrain-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-SRAM-Apex-drivetrain-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-SRAM-Apex-drivetrain-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-SRAM-Apex-drivetrain-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-rear-dropout.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"661\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-rear-dropout.jpeg\" alt=\"Marin Bikes Four Corners 2 rear dropout\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-rear-dropout.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-rear-dropout-297x153.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-rear-dropout-800x413.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-rear-dropout-120x62.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-rear-dropout-768x397.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It’s also rocking a SRAM Apex 1×12-speed drive train, hydraulic bracks, and tubeless compatible rims and tires. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-along-the-beach-e1708720835280.jpeg\"><img width=\"908\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-along-the-beach-e1708720835280.jpeg\" alt=\"Marin Bikes Four Corners 2 along the beach\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-along-the-beach-e1708720835280.jpeg 908w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-along-the-beach-e1708720835280-213x300.jpeg 213w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-along-the-beach-e1708720835280-800x1128.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-along-the-beach-e1708720835280-85x120.jpeg 85w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-along-the-beach-e1708720835280-768x1083.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-in-the-woods--e1708720816753.jpeg\"><img width=\"851\" height=\"1132\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-in-the-woods--e1708720816753.jpeg\" alt=\"Marin Bikes Four Corners 2 in the woods\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-in-the-woods--e1708720816753.jpeg 851w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-in-the-woods--e1708720816753-226x300.jpeg 226w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-in-the-woods--e1708720816753-800x1064.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-in-the-woods--e1708720816753-90x120.jpeg 90w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-in-the-woods--e1708720816753-768x1022.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Geometry for the Four Corners 2 is said to follow the tracks of the Four Corners 1. But, the 70°-71° HTA (depending on size) runs a lil’ more progressive than a typical touring bike. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-dropper-routing.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-dropper-routing.jpeg\" alt=\"Marin Bikes Four Corners 2 dropper routing\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-dropper-routing.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-dropper-routing-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-dropper-routing-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-dropper-routing-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-dropper-routing-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-dropper-routing-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Seat tubes are routed and ready for dropper posts if that strikes your fancy. The handlebars are wider as well, at 440-460mm. Both the wheel sizes for the Four Corners 2, (650b for XS and S / 700c for M, L, XL) roll on 44mm wide tires but have frame clearance for up to 50mm.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-action-nipples.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-action-nipples.jpeg\" alt=\"Marin Bikes Four Corners 2 action nipples\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-action-nipples.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-action-nipples-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-action-nipples-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-action-nipples-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-action-nipples-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-action-nipples-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-top-tube-nips.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-top-tube-nips.jpeg\" alt=\"Marin Bikes Four Corners 2 top tube nips\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-top-tube-nips.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-top-tube-nips-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-top-tube-nips-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-top-tube-nips-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-top-tube-nips-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-top-tube-nips-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Four Corners 2 Retail and Features</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-ready-for-adventure.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-ready-for-adventure.jpeg\" alt=\"Marin Bikes Four Corners 2 ready for adventure\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-ready-for-adventure.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-ready-for-adventure-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-ready-for-adventure-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-ready-for-adventure-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-ready-for-adventure-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-ready-for-adventure-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-going-fast.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-going-fast.jpeg\" alt=\"Marin Bikes Four Corners 2 going fast\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-going-fast.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-going-fast-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-going-fast-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-going-fast-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-going-fast-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-going-fast-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $1,999</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Series 3 double-butted CroMo frame and fork, with size-specific wheel sizes for proper fit</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Front and rear thru-axles</li>\n\n\n\n<li>SRAM Apex 1×12 wide-range drivetrain</li>\n\n\n\n<li>SRAM Apex hydraulic disc brakes</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Vee Tire Co Rocket Man 44mm tubeless-compatible tires</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-descent.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"849\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-descent.jpeg\" alt=\"Marin Bikes Four Corners 2 descent\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-descent.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-descent-297x197.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-descent-800x531.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-descent-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Marin-Bikes-Four-Corners-2-descent-768x509.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.marinbikes.com/\" target=\"_blank\">MarinBikes.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/marin-four-corners-2-adventure-touring-bike/\">Marin Launches New Four Corners 2 an Affordable Up-Spec’d Adventure Tourer</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"a5b8b8f73b01709c61e9521b91b0c9a0f7bbd04b359f4c48341deadbca5fb4ce","category":"Cycling"}